Introduction

Get ready to experience the thrill of managing traffic in Traffic Mania! Developed by OpenAI, this exciting strategy game puts you in control of a bustling city's traffic flow. Your task is to prevent accidents and ensure a smooth ride for vehicles as you navigate through challenging intersections. Brace yourself for a road management adventure like no other!
